<h5><a href="?PHPSESSID=992e616df58c4135afa9fbba6c7c220a&amp;board=542.0">王牌进化区</a> / <a href="?PHPSESSID=992e616df58c4135afa9fbba6c7c220a&amp;topic=127521.msg1130075#msg1130075" rel="nofollow">人物卡——王越</a></h5>
